                    <h2 id="focusing-on-the-user" class="__title invisible">Focusing on the User</h2>
                    </div>

  
  <p>User needs drive all of the content and services that make up the web presence. All web content and services are regularly assessed through user testing and use data. Areas of the web presence that do not meet the standards of our users are retired or improved.</p>



  
